a><div class="nav-submenu"> <a class="nav-link-sub-toggle i-arrow-left js_toggle visible-sm visible-xs" data-target=".nav-main">Voltar</a> <a class="nav-link-spot i-arrow-right-after" href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/ajude-o-cicv">Panorama sobre Como ajudar</a><div class=" nav-split"><ul><li><h5 class="h5">Faça já sua doação</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/donate" title="">Doação do Brasil</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/doar" title="">Doação de outros países</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/faq/doar-ao-cicv-perguntas-mais-frequentes" title="">Perguntas mais frequentes</a></li></ul></li><li><h5 class="h5">Outras formas de ajudar</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/ajude-o-cicv/audience/amigos-do-cicv" title="">Amigos do CICV</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/ajude-o-cicv/audience/filantropia" title="">Filantropia</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/ajude-o-cicv/audience/herancas-e-legados" title="">Heranças e legados</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/ajude-o-cicv/audience/parcerias-com-sua-fundacao" title="">Parcerias com a sua fundação</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/ajude-o-cicv/audience/parcerias-corporativas" title="">Parcerias corporativas</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container pull-right hidden-xs hidden-sm"> <a href="https://doe.cicv.org.br/institucional/?utm_source=institucional&utm_medium=site-cicv&utm_campaign=institucional-DM" class="bg-red nav-link-main">Faça já sua doação</a></div></div></div></div> </nav></div><div class="region region-content"><div id="fullpage"> <section class="clearfix section first-section " id="what-we-do"><div class="wwd-inner"><div class="header-wrapper visible-sm visible-xs"><header class="site-header"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4 slogan-logo"><div class="logo-wrapper"><div id="logo"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt" class="logo"><img src="/sites/default/themes/icrc_theme/images/pt/logo-small.png" alt="Comitê Internacional da Cruz Vermelha"/></a></div><div class="slogan font-sm-18"><h1 class="font-sm-18"> Comitê Internacional da Cruz Vermelha</h1></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-8 right-content"><div class="visible-sm visible-xs list-languages"> <select class="styled-language-select i-arrow-down-after redirection-select"><option value="https://www.icrc.org/pt" selected="selected">PT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en">EN</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/fr">FR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/es">ES</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/zh">ZH</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ar">AR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ru">RU</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/de">DE</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/it">IT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/languages">Outros</option> </select></div></div></div></div></header></div><div class="fill section-first-main"><div class="video-section"><div class="video-wrapper responsive-video-container video-available"> <video data-keepplaying data-autoplay loop muted poster="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT"> <source data-src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/homepage_files/what-we-do-video_0.mp4" type="video/mp4" /> </video><div class="image"> <img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT" alt="icrc-car-syria"/></div><div class="video-text-wrapper"><div class="video-text"> <a href="/pt/what-we-do/video" class="lightbox-embed-video youtube"><span class="thumbnail-video-button"></span></a><div class="main-text">No terreno em mais de 90 países, somos o Comitê Internacional da Cruz Vermelha, uma organização neutra, imparcial e independente.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="text-section"><div clas